cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with computer vision and pattern recognition using deep learning techniques to predict crime rates from satellite imagery. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with crime prevention and safety, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of deep learning techniques for prediction falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves data analysis and prediction, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
